#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.183-352"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.183-352:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.183-352:0.2"
msgid "18. Rāgapeyyāla"
msgstr "19. Abbreviated Texts Beginning with Greed"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.183-352:0.3"
msgid "183–​352"
msgstr "183–​352"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.183-352:1.1"
msgid "“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr "“For insight into greed, three things should be developed."

msgctxt "an3.183-352:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.183-352:1.3"
msgid "Suññato samādhi, animitto samādhi, appaṇihito samādhi—"
msgstr "Emptiness immersion; signless immersion; undirected immersion."

#. VAR: () → (rāgassa bhikkhave abhiññāya tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā. katame tayo? savitakkasavicāro samādhi, avitakkavicāramatto immersion, avitakkaavicāro samādhi. rāgassa bhikkhave abhiññāya ime tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā.) etthantare pāṭho katthaci dissati, aṭṭhakathāyaṃ
msgctxt "an3.183-352:1.4"
msgid "rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya ime tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā. (1) ()"
msgstr "For insight into greed, these three things should be developed."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.183-352:2.1"
msgid "Rāgassa, bhikkhave, pariññāya … pe …"
msgstr "For the complete understanding of greed …"

msgctxt "an3.183-352:2.2"
msgid "parikkhayāya …"
msgstr "complete ending …"

msgctxt "an3.183-352:2.3"
msgid "pahānāya …"
msgstr "giving up …"

msgctxt "an3.183-352:2.4"
msgid "khayāya …"
msgstr "ending …"

msgctxt "an3.183-352:2.5"
msgid "vayāya …"
msgstr "vanishing …"

msgctxt "an3.183-352:2.6"
msgid "virāgāya …"
msgstr "fading away …"

msgctxt "an3.183-352:2.7"
msgid "nirodhāya …"
msgstr "cessation …"

